OL,3,CFormer police officer nicknamed 'the
OL,4,Coctopus' sacked for gross misconduct
OL,6,FA former senior police officer who was
OL,7,Fnicknamed "the octopus" for his
OL,8,Fbehaviour towards women has been
OL,9,Fsacked for gross misconduct.
OL,11,FSuperintendent Gary Davies, of Dyfed-
OL,12,FPowys Police, had been accused of
OL,13,Fengaging in inappropriate and
OL,14,Fmisogynistic behaviour towards female
OL,15,Fcolleagues.
OL,17,FHe was suspended in July 2022
OL,18,Ffollowing allegations about his
OL,19,Fconduct between 2017 and 2020.
