OL,3,CFormer police officer nicknamed 'the
OL,4,Coctopus' sacked for gross misconduct
OL,6,FFollowing a two-week disciplinary
OL,7,Fhearing at police HQ in
OL,8,FCarmarthenshire, the allegations were
OL,9,Ffound proven against him.
OL,11,FIt heard Mr Davies had touched two
OL,12,Fwomen at a Christmas party without
OL,13,Ftheir permission, and making
OL,14,Finappropriate comments comparing women
OL,15,Fto brands of car, such as Ferrari,
OL,16,FRolls Royce or Porsche.
OL,18,FMr Davies told the panel he had no
OL,19,Fknowledge of being nicknamed "the
OL,20,Foctopus" by female colleagues
