OL,4,Coctopus' sacked for gross misconduct
OL,6,FThe hearing, which was chaired by
OL,7,Flawyer Oliver Thorne, found he had
OL,8,Fbreached the standards of professional
OL,9,Fbehaviour relating to authority,
OL,10,Frespect and courtesy, discreditable
OL,11,Fconduct, and equality and diversity.
OL,13,FHe was dismissed from Dyfed-Powys
OL,14,FPolice and added to the College of
OL,15,FPolicing barred list.
OL,17,FDeputy Chief Constable Ifan Charles
OL,18,Fapologised to the victims of Mr Davies
OL,19,Fand said his conduct was unacceptable.
