OL,6,F"Dyfed-Powys Police expects the
OL,7,Fhighest standards of professional
OL,8,Fbehaviour from its officers and staff,
OL,9,Fboth on and off duty ` and even more
OL,10,Fso for its senior leadership team," he
OL,11,Fsaid.
OL,13,F"I apologise to the former and current
OL,14,Fstaff and officers who were victimised
OL,15,Fby former Superintendent Gary Davies's
OL,16,Finappropriate behaviour and thank them
OL,17,Ffor their courage in reporting his
OL,18,Fmisconduct.
