OL,6,F"We've heard the experiences of a
OL,7,Fnumber of colleagues and former
OL,8,Fcolleagues over the past two weeks,
OL,9,Fthe majority of whom are women who
OL,10,Fsuffered from his misogynistic
OL,11,Fbehaviour during the course of their
OL,12,Fduties.
OL,14,F"They are role models, and I thank
OL,15,Fthem for the integrity and courage
OL,16,Fthey have shown in this difficult and
OL,17,Funacceptable situation.
