OL,6,F"I appreciate this case is shocking,
OL,7,Fand it may cause concern to the
OL,8,Fpublic. I would like to reassure you
OL,9,Fthat swift action was taken to suspend
OL,10,Fformer Superintendent Gary Davies once
OL,11,Fallegations were made, and that the
OL,12,Fcase has been treated with utmost
OL,13,Fseriousness.
