OL,6,F"The outcome of today's hearing is
OL,7,Freflective of this approach, and I
OL,8,Fhope reassures the public that Dyfed-
OL,9,FPowys Police will do all it can to
OL,10,Fmaintain the high standards rightly
OL,11,Fexpected of police officers and staff
OL,12,F` particularly those in senior
OL,13,Fpositions.
OL,15,F"As a force, we will use all of the
OL,16,Ftools available to us to ensure the
OL,17,Fefficient and swift manner of
OL,18,Fdismissing those who should no longer
OL,19,Fhold the office of constable."
