OL,6,FPolice and Crime Commissioner Dafydd
OL,7,FLlywelyn added: "The public rightly
OL,8,Fexpects the highest standards from
OL,9,Fthose who serve in policing.
OL,11,F"Former Superintendent Gary Davies
OL,12,Factions fell short of these
OL,13,Fexpectations, and their dismissal
OL,14,Freflects our commitment to integrity,
OL,15,Fprofessionalism, and public trust.
OL,17,F"There is no place in Dyfed-Powys
OL,18,FPolice for those who undermine these
OL,19,Fvalues."
